{"tid":368360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★女囚犯死亡】自言自語高聲叫囂　狂咳吐血送院　六日後不治","createTime":"2017-08-21T13:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T14:48:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"09060c58264e2ca5eaef5ff6e8d5a48231823b4e","tid":368360,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:12:10.000Z","msg":"大欖女懲教所女性還押在囚人士今日於屯醫因病不治。一名38歲女子於本月12日因違反逗留條件罪，被還押大欖女懲教所。她被還押三日後，即上周二(15日)下午3時45分，該名在囚女子突然在囚室內自言自語及大聲叫囂，未幾突然咳嗽並吐血，當時她仍然清醒。懲教署職員即時為她進行治療，並召支援人員到場。該名在囚女子經初步治療後，被送往屯門醫院治理。她留醫六日後，情況急轉直下，至今(21日)上午10時52分證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署發言人指，已將事件通知警方，死因裁判法庭亦將進行死因研訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/113565/-女囚犯死亡-自言自語高聲叫囂-狂咳吐血送院-六日後不治\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F113565%2F-%E5%A5%B3%E5%9B%9A%E7%8A%AF%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E8%87%AA%E8%A8%80%E8%87%AA%E8%AA%9E%E9%AB%98%E8%81%B2%E5%8F%AB%E5%9B%82-%E7%8B%82%E5%92%B3%E5%90%90%E8%A1%80%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB&d=ZXOFqNCCuWIl91%2F%2FYo6SXr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5fd16acc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/113565/-女囚犯死亡-自言自語高聲叫囂-狂咳吐血送院-六日後不治</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ae224c8383e6d526ff1cba063a3a83aa72b43b","tid":368360,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a3b58ecdde0cab1d2f98b6cf32d3dfb9d8de7f","tid":368360,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:17:47.000Z","msg":"冇返工就出事"},{"pid":